rious social activities, ranging from bingo games to life cycle rituals and, most significantly, to join the dignitaries in their council meetings of a Kanak Confederation. By transferring the gifts expected from the participants on all such occasions he demonstrates his acknowledgement of the authority of the Kanak and their ancestors, an essential step towards his integration in Kanak society.\"}]}');
